Property details

At the storied address of 2200 Pacific Avenue, this Pacific Heights residence delivers a caliber of living rarely found in San Francisco. An effortless pied--terre blends privacy, provenance, and architectural distinction in one iconic setting. And did we mention the only roof top pool wit... h panoramic views of the Bridge. This nearly 1000 square-foot One Bedroom opens directly to an additional 1,200-square-foot private and exclusive use courtyard! It creates an indoor-outdoor experience more reminiscent of a European villa than a city condominium. Positioned on the main level with no stairs, this residence offers seamless accessibility without compromising elegancean exceptional advantage rarely paired with luxury. The building has a full-service doorman to welcome residents, while interior reflect a refined, timeless sensibility. Rare, gracious, and quietly iconic, 2200 Pacific is not simply a residence. It is a statement address, designed for those who value discretion, beauty, and an elevated San Francisco lifestyle. It is a Beverly Hills Hotel like-vibe but with the pool on the roof! ** note the price per sq ft does not take into account the 1200 sq ft exclusive courtyard **
